Product Concept

ChainLink AI

A universal AI supply-chain coordination platform.

Instead of every company having isolated ERPs and emailing spreadsheets back and forth, ChainLink sits in the middle and:
	•	connects customers
	•	connects suppliers
	•	connects distributors
	•	connects logistics providers
	•	connects warehouses

And AI manages the communication, order flow, and problem resolution.

⸻

Core Idea

Supply chains today look like this:

Customer -> Distributor -> Manufacturer -> Supplier
         -> Logistics -> Warehouse -> Retailer

But communication happens through:
	•	email
	•	PDFs
	•	EDI
	•	spreadsheets
	•	phone calls
	•	different ERPs

So things break constantly.

Your SaaS becomes the AI layer that translates and coordinates everything.

